  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <section id="introduction">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="section-heading">Introduction</h2>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">What is a 'Blender AR Nano Film' and why should you participate?</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-film fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
          <h4 class="service-heading">What is a 'Blender AR Nano Film'?</h4>
          <p class="text-muted">A 'Blender AR Nano Film' is a 3D art and animation piece created with Blender and displayed in Augmented Reality using free and open source tools like MindAR, three.js and GitHub. It is a fun and innovative way to express and share your creativity with the world.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-trophy fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
          <h4 class="service-heading">What is the 'Free Opening of the Blender AR Nano Film Festival'?</h4>
          <p class="text-muted">The 'Free Opening of the Blender AR Nano Film Festival' is an initiative that invites you to participate in a contest where you can create and show your own 'Blender AR Nano Film' using Blender and WebAR. You can join solo or in collaboration with other artists.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-users fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
          <h4 class="service-heading">Who is this initiative for?</h4>
          <p class="text-muted">This initiative is for anyone who uses Blender and is a digital artist, an illustrator, a designer, an animator, a teacher, a writer, a musician or a creative. No matter if you are an expert or a novice, all you need is the desire to create and share. The important thing is that you have fun.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-heart fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
          <h4 class="service-heading">Why should you participate?</h4>
          <p class="text-muted">You should participate in this initiative because you will learn new skills, discover new possibilities, express your art, connect with other artists, and have a chance to win prizes and recognition.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

