        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="section-heading">Testimony</h2>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">How did Blender and WebAR save my life?</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12">
