            <h4 class="subheading">The darkest year of my life</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-body">
            <p class="text-muted">I was diagnosed with post-pandemic depression, a condition that affected many people after the COVID-19 crisis. I felt hopeless, lonely and sad. I had no motivation to do anything.</p>
