            </div>
            <div class="timeline-body">
              <p class="text-muted">One day, I found Pierrick Picaut on the internet and his course "Alive! Blender animation course". I decided to give it a try and I enrolled in his course. It was the best decision of my life.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-image">
          <img class="img-circle img-responsive" src="img/about/3.jpg" alt="">
