            <h4 class="subheading">The best year of my life</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-body">
            <p class="text-muted">His course taught me how to use Blender to create amazing 3D animations. He also taught me how to use WebAR to display my animations in Augmented Reality. He was a great teacher and a great person. He inspired me, supported me and encouraged me.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-inverted">
          <div class="timeline-image">
