            <div class="timeline-heading">
              <h4>2023</h4>
              <h4 class="subheading">The present year of my life</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-body">
              <p class="text-muted">Thanks to his course, I discovered a new passion and a new purpose. I started to create my own 'Blender AR Nano Films' and to share them with the world. I also started to feel better, happier and more alive.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
